flowchart TB
    Internet((Internet))
    IGW[Internet Gateway]
    subgraph Insp["Inspection VPC - 2 AZs"]
      direction TB
      NAT[NAT Gateways x2]
      NFW[Network Firewall x2 AZs]
      FWRT[Firewall route tables per AZ]
      TGWRT[TGW attach route tables per AZ]
    end
    TGW[Transit Gateway]

    subgraph Prod["Production VPC - 2 AZs"]
      PRODAPP[Private app subnets]
    end
    subgraph Dev["Development VPC - 2 AZs"]
      DEVAPP[Private app subnets]
    end
    subgraph Shared["Shared Services VPC - 2 AZs"]
      SHAPP[Private shared subnets]
    end

    PRODAPP -->|0.0.0.0/0| TGW
    DEVAPP -->|0.0.0.0/0| TGW
    SHAPP -->|0.0.0.0/0| TGW
    TGW -->|workload rt default| TGWRT
    TGWRT -->|0.0.0.0/0 per AZ| NFW
    NFW --> FWRT
    FWRT -->|0.0.0.0/0 per AZ| NAT
    FWRT -.->|spoke CIDRs| TGW
    NAT --> IGW
    IGW --> Internet
    Internet -.->|return via NAT, symmetric AZ| NAT